Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\b0\fs52.5\frz342.5\pos(948,493.8)}跟蹤順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕  你流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要趕快做點處理才行
